<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <style>
      body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          background-color: #f4f6f9;
          color: #333;
          padding: 30px;
      }

      .container {
          background-color: #ffffff;
          border-radius: 8px;
          box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          max-width: 600px;
          margin: auto;
          padding: 30px;
      }

      h2 {
          color: #d9534f;
          font-size: 24px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      p {
          font-size: 16px;
          line-height: 1.6;
          margin: 15px 0;
      }

      .footer {
          margin-top: 30px;
          font-size: 14px;
          color: #999;
          text-align: center;
      }

      .btn {
          display: inline-block;
          margin-top: 20px;
          padding: 10px 20px;
          background-color: #0275d8;
          color: #fff;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 4px;
      }

      .btn:hover {
          background-color: #025aa5;
      }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
  <h2>Goodbye <%= @user.first_name.present? ? @user.first_name : @user.email %>,</h2>

  <p>We're sorry to see you leave <strong>Movie Review</strong>. Your account has been successfully cancelled, and all your data has been removed.</p>

  <p>If this was a mistake, or if you ever feel like revisiting our movie-loving community, you're always welcome to rejoin us. We'd love to have you back!</p>

  <p>Until then, take care and happy watching ðŸŽ¬</p>

  <a href="<%= root_url %>" class="btn">Visit Movie Review</a>

  <div class="footer">
    If you have any feedback or questions, feel free to reply to this email.<br>
    &copy; <%= Time.current.year %> Movie Review. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
